data.description: This stunning traditional-style home is nestled in the sought after neighborhood of Windsor Hill. The large inviting screened in front porch is perfect for some rocking chairs and relaxing with your favorite beverage. Upon entry, you are greeted with laminate floors and smooth ceilings. The spacious living room features a wood burning fireplace, perfect for cozy nights in during chilly winter months. The eat-in kitchen is adorned with a pull out shelf system, dazzling granite countertops and updated appliances. The upstairs master bedroom is complete with multiple closets, and an en-suite bathroom. Take a step out back and enjoy the in-ground saltwater pool, great for entertaining family and friends while you grill out on the back patio, or for just cooling down on a hot summer day.This home is conveniently located near local shopping, dining and entertainment options including Northwoods Mall, Tanger Outlets and Frankie's Fun Park. Don't wait! Come see this home today!  *Refrigerator, washer and dryer to convey with acceptable offer and as part of the sales contract.**
